  "description": "<ul><li>🌟 We’re Hiring: Restaurant Service Staff / Waiter 🌟</li></ul><p>📍 HarbourFront MRT (NE1 – Purple Line)</p><ul><li>🏢 Industry: Food Services (Chain Restaurant)</li></ul><p>💰 Salary & Benefits</p><ul><li>Basic Salary: SGD 3,000</li><li>Monthly Off Days: 6 days</li><li>Annual & Sick Leave: In accordance with MOM regulations</li></ul><p>⏰ Working Hours</p><ul><li>9:30 AM – 2:00 PM</li><li>4:30 PM – 10:00 PM</li></ul><p>(Comfortable split shift in a fully air-conditioned working environment)</p><p>🍽 About the Role We are a well-established chain restaurant with a positive and supportive work culture, looking for an experienced Restaurant Service Staff / Waiter to join our team and deliver excellent dining experiences to our customers.</p><p>🔑 Responsibilities</p><ul><li>Take customer orders accurately and serve food and beverages promptly to ensure smooth dining flow</li><li>Monitor and respond to customer needs throughout their dining experience to maintain high satisfaction levels</li><li>Collaborate with team members to support daily restaurant operations and maintain service standards</li><li>Follow company service procedures and hygiene standards to ensure a safe and welcoming environment</li><li>Handle customer inquiries and resolve issues efficiently to uphold the restaurant’s reputation</li></ul><p>✅ Required Competencies</p><ul><li>Demonstrated experience in restaurant or F&B service roles to perform core service tasks effectively</li><li>Ability to work efficiently in a fast-paced F&B environment while maintaining quality service</li><li>Strong customer service skills to engage customers positively and meet their dining expectations</li><li>Proactive and responsible work approach to contribute reliably to team operations</li><li>Teamwork skills to cooperate with colleagues and support a positive work atmosphere</li></ul>",
